General.Name: MCS Services Ltd
General.Description: MCS Services Limited, together with its subsidiaries, provides security services in Australia. The company also provides security alarm and CCTV systems tailored for business or home, as well as loss prevention solutions It serves various industries, such as retail, event, educational, marine, industrial, healthcare. The company was founded in 2005 and is headquartered in Joondalup, Australia.
